pe=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/fe99f155ac06e4948844b0aa79991c03.mp4?t=1726210564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/e94fd70ff88cd29ed331575707c4939f.poster.avif?t=1726210564\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/e94fd70ff88cd29ed331575707c4939f.webm?t=1726210564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/e94fd70ff88cd29ed331575707c4939f.mp4?t=1726210564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slash Into Hell</h2>As the Revenge Agent of Heaven, you will be able to use more than 3 classes, 12 types of weapon to slash among demons.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4 Chapters, over 20 types of monsters</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/030f1f65820e4cdfdaa21f3694000291.avif?t=1726210564\" width=600 height=1152 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Growing Power of Weapon</h2>Kill demons to collect gems, and then turn gems into rune inlays for your weapon. The runes could provide various of new abilities to contribute to your battle style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/94c9e2c90553a294763bc9eb8f6bd971.poster.avif?t=1726210564\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/94c9e2c90553a294763bc9eb8f6bd971.webm?t=1726210564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/94c9e2c90553a294763bc9eb8f6bd971.mp4?t=1726210564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Death Is Beginning</h2>If you die in a fight, the weapon is also lost with all the runes inlay. Your can start another challenge and if lucky enough, you could find the lost weapon.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Permanent Upgrade</h2>Win or lose, when you reborn back to heaven, all the gems you collect along the way will turn to dust. Make use of these dust to unlock permanent upgrade.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/ca840b2f7b1dcee0ffd3f86197d542f0.avif?t=1726210564\" width=600 height=323 /></span>",
